            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-c3a89cb6-b3b9-4ecf-bc62-04ba5ba2da56" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
