<p class="">Will the right hon. Gentleman seize the opportunity tomorrow of making the situation a little clearer, because the situation which does exist now is a danger to the lives of a great many British subjects out there, and can possibly be separated from the question of recognition? It would allay the fears and anxieties if some sort of progress report were to be made.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
