<p class="">I think my answers today have made it pretty clear, and I shall not have much time tomorrow to deal with all the world. If the hon. Gentleman reads the answers given today, he will see that I am following this thing through methodically and I am hoping to produce a good result. I do not think there are any British lives actually in danger in Shanghai at the moment, so far as I know.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-225b9418-b218-48c9-9136-bfdb4dcacdc0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
